::KitKat::

She looked down at the floor, but saw the horror and pain that had 
been caused.  She couldn't beleive it.  She sat down and still saw 
the images of terror that Phobia had wrought to others.  She saw what 
could have happened to her and the others in her group.  She shook 
her head and then yelled out, "ENOUGH!"  She closed her eyes and 
covered her face with her hands. She whispered,"I've seen enough."  
She looked at Death, "You've proved well that he was a evil and vile 
as you said." She looked down and couldn't help it as a sinlge tear 
ran down her face. The feeling of such betrayal just consumed 
her,"plea." she coughed to clear her throat." Please check the others 
for the same thing. I can't have this happen and jeopardize the 
others here. I can't have such," she stopped and looked at the 
body,"such a bot here and risk all the others in our team."  she just 
sat there, looking at the body.
